[3.7V LiPo Battery (1000mAh)]
    + (Positive) ----> [TP4056 Charger Module OUT+]
    - (Negative) ----> [TP4056 Charger Module OUT-]
    
[TP4056 Charger Module]
    OUT+ ----> [PSoC™ 6 AI Kit VIN (5V-tolerant)]
    OUT- ----> [PSoC™ 6 AI Kit GND]
    USB-C Input <---- [USB-C Cable for Charging]

[PSoC™ 6 AI Evaluation Kit (CY8CKIT-062S2-AI)]
    VIN: Receives 3.7V from TP4056
    GND: Ground connection
    Onboard Sensors:
        - MEMS Microphone (IM72D128): Audio input for sound detection
        - IMU (Bosch BMI-270/BMM-350): Movement detection
        - Barometric Pressure Sensor (DPS368): Environmental monitoring
        - Wi-Fi/BLE Module (Murata LBEE5KL1YN): Alert transmission
    USB-C Port <---- [USB-C Cable for Programming/Debugging]
